134. Memorandum From the Deputy Assistant Secretary of State for Near Eastern,
                    South Asian, and African Affairs (Jernegan) to the Deputy Under Secretary of State (Matthews)Source: National Archives, RG 59, Central Files 1950–1954, 888.2553/10–2352. Top Secret;
                        Security Information. Drafted by Jernegan. Copies were sent to Richards, Beale, Berry, and Roosevelt.
